## 🔐 Security Highlights
- Face ID + fingerprint login
- End-to-end encrypted chats
- Emergency location alerts
- Parental controls and fraud detection

## 🧪 Roadmap
- AR filters for immersive content
- NFT rewards for digital ownership
- Creator Academy for skill development
- Smart TV & wearable support
- Charity challenges and global reach


